				<wikidot:authorName>fieldstone</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1436137</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Sometimes we do the wrong things for the right reasons.</p> <p>This is for the first round of the OCT tournament; <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/ethics">Agent Johnson</a> vs. <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1233">Moon Champion</a>. Cadavercommander and fieldstone: two tastes that go together like blood and diesel.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536130522" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536130522" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" >not_a_seagull</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/magnadeus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3499685&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536130522" alt="magnadeus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3499685)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/magnadeus" >magnadeus</a></span> for feedback. Feel like I'm forgetting someone so let me know if that's you. Also thanks <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536130522" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" >CadaverCommander</a></span> for inventing Moon Champion and generally being a good bro and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1536130522" alt="PeppersGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" >PeppersGhost</a></span> for organizing this thing.</p> <p>Link to CC's tale will go here when he posts it. Pictures are from:<br /> <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/usnationalarchives/3660777810">https://www.flickr.com/photos/usnationalarchives/3660777810</a><br /> <a href="https://picryl.com/media/joseph-brown-house-50-south-main-street-providence-providence-county-ri-4">https://picryl.com/media/joseph-brown-house-50-south-main-street-providence-providence-county-ri-4</a><br /> <a href="https://pxhere.com/en/photo/1087338">https://pxhere.com/en/photo/1087338</a><br /> <a href="https://www.nellis.af.mil/News/Article/1171564/9th-civil-engineer-squadron-conquer-darkness-confined-spaces/">https://www.nellis.af.mil/News/Article/1171564/9th-civil-engineer-squadron-conquer-darkness-confined-spaces/</a></p> <p>Remember, you are loved.</p> 
